{"tid":1057272,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"［愛情短故][真人真事] 一個肥仔係中學嘅愛情故事","createTime":"2019-03-11T18:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-14T16:25:34.000Z","uid":57072,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81a63cc243ad420baa4173c44b7d28ec14b4714a","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:32:52.000Z","msg":"呢個故係根據我個朋友嘅經歷作出黎 大家可以當九成真一成假咁睇 為左方便大家睇 故事都會以第一身角度&rdquo;我&rdquo;做出發點 呢個故係想講一個肥仔由肥仔瘦左之後變左仆街 再變好嘅故事 細佬第一次出故 文筆有錯嘅大家屌細力啲"},{"pid":"e941709220163395c5be0ce77a78bc5f0add660e","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:33:33.000Z","msg":"我係一個肥仔 一個係學校完全唔顯眼嘅肥仔 而且仲好自卑 小五個年試過暗戀一個女仔兩年都唔敢表白 睇住佢同左其他人一齊仲要祝福佢 諗起真係得啖笑 作為一個肥仔 所謂溝女只不過係幻想 每日都等個天跌條女比自己 中二試過同一個女仔曖味 但都係自卑 最後咩都無講出口 直到我中三 竟然比我遇到佢...我嘅初戀"},{"pid":"421aa9e737775a65801f9513cdae60baa0ee2b3a","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9930009582374e37070507f3be01ee484c6419c8","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dc8b8131eac07b251f7ee425da9c0840fe3869f","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T18:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4955ff328688a94380bed68df815d888773e67","tid":1057272,"uid":34084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T19:32:31.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0243655813c5c747b92dc4336e96d6eb5a7d837","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a4955ff328688a94380bed68df815d888773e67","tid":1057272,"uid":34084,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T19:3