-03-12T00:17:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1a8b1687436328da60beb854c20131c459a98a","tid":1057272,"uid":170630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"死肥閪"},{"pid":"3a9e76ca6ed10a866521d04718eaf8052db7e74d","tid":1057272,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"出得太慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567b55e69fa8af1358e41b037aefd183958c1b77","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"之後嘅一個月 大家傾計都頻密左 內容都有曖昧 但係佢一直都無同我表白 只不過做啲嘢真係好明顯 例如我唔搵或者無覆佢 佢就開下頹post咁樣 我又係好怕醜嘅人 同埋已經當左佢係好朋友 所以一直都無行前一步 我無諗過一個肥仔竟然真係有女仔鍾意 我依家諗起都覺得好誇張 我最肥果陣係上到11x kg 問心我都唔會鍾意一個肥婆 無論性格幾咁好 呢個情況維持左一個幾月 直到我終於夠膽約佢出街睇戲"},{"pid":"b2823302aa7ab515d17cf51a1341c0a66fb1096d","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a9e76ca6ed10a866521d04718eaf8052db7e74d","tid":1057272,"uid":68902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"出得太慢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:46:12.000Z","msg":"Sorry啊 有啲忙"},{"pid":"689cac58cb0a81ce3de8965ad834cebd0c86392b","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:49:49.000Z","msg":"題外話 呢個女仔已經變左我個ex 我地一齊左幾年 佢係一個好女仔 係我浪費左佢 其實呢個故會出現都係因為我未放底佢 想藉此懷念下我地嘅一點一滴 同埋為我做過嘅錯事反省一下"},{"pid":"4871117c61607f123a1741bc1a9ed9a0e3772b36","tid":1057272,"uid":57072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-12T17:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class